      "rationale": "GCI study (ValidationResult morrison-vr-02) demonstrated GCI of 3.1% for wall shear stress on the 28.4M-cell fine mesh. Discretization error level 2 satisfied. Study was performed at adult flow conditions; the assessment team judges the mesh topology adequate for the extended paediatric flow range given geometric similarity of flow structures at lower Reynolds numbers."
