      "rationale": "In-vitro test rig used phosphate-buffered saline with bovine erythrocytes at 37 °C, matching CFD boundary conditions. Pump speed controlled to ±10 RPM. Test condition fidelity documented in laboratory test report TR-2022-04. Conditions cover adult operating points; paediatric conditions were not tested but are considered bounded by the adult dataset."
