      "rationale": "Across five adult validation points, CFD-predicted RH agreed with measurement within ±12% (maximum deviation 11.8% at 2.5 L/min). Systematic bias estimated at 2.3%. Output comparison level 2 satisfied per ValidationResult morrison-vr-01."
