    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 at MRL 2. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The post-clearance extension of the indicated patient population to include paediatric patients at 1.2–2.0 L/min was reviewed; the assessment team concluded that the existing validation evidence from the adult flow range is physically representative and bounding for the paediatric sub-range, and that no additional experimental validation is required prior to use within the expanded envelope. Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance level.",
